data.description: Looking for that the Right Home?  This Is It!!! 3/3/2 Located in High and Dry Cinnamon Ridge Preserve!!! Two of the bedrooms designed as master suites, each with its own attached bathroom for added privacy and convenience. A central living room and Dining Room serves as a common area for family and guests. The Kitchen opens up ta a separate family room that could be a cozy space for family members to spend quality time, play games, or enjoy recreational activities.  Unwind  on your back patio to enjoy a cozy sitting area, for relaxation and conversation, while grilling out in your back yard. Head out to main road and see that you are convenient to head in on direction and be in Homosassa to spend time at the Wild Life Park or head in the other direction for either Crystal River for diving or spending time with the Manatee's.  Easy access to the Parkway for major shopping  Seller has assumable mortgage at 2.25%  30 year note.  Call for details!!!
